---
title: Pepper-Crusted Steak with Warm Potato and Sugar Snap Pea Salad
description: Our peppercorn crust pulls no punches. It’s time for this seasoning to shine, as you enjoy hints of citrus, mustard and even sweetness pepper can offer. We’ve softened the blow with our creamy potato salad - crunchy sugar snap peas and dill add sophistication.
